data.description: Step into a world of charm and comfort with this spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home! This property offers a warm, welcoming atmosphere that you'll instantly fall in love with. The living area is the heart of this home. Whether you're spending quality time with loved ones, hosting friends, or enjoying a quiet evening by the fireplace, this room is designed to accommodate all your needs. The kitchen is a true gem, featuring modern countertops and backsplash plus plenty of storage for your culinary needs. This home is perfect for hosting all your gatherings! Whether you dream of gardening or nestling up in the cozy patio out front, the outdoor space offers endless possibilities. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this spacious, delightful home your own. It's the perfect blend of space and style, ideal for anyone who values comfort and charm.
